response.overview: After clearing brush for the government, a group of men return to town claiming their friend was abducted their friend. Despite no apparent motive or evidence of foul play, no-one believes their story and his disappearance is treated as murder.
response.tagline: Alien abduction. November 5, 1975. White Mountains, Northeastern Arizona.
